Package: cdspeedctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Universal CD-ROM speed limiter for whisper-quiet audio playback
 A lightweight utility to limit CD-ROM read speed using ioctl or raw SCSI commands.
 Designed for low-power systems with USB optical drives, ideal for bit-perfect
 playback with minimal mechanical noise.
